data.description: Beautiful home- So much space, privacy and one of a kind front elevation for this neighborhood. New roof, newer HVACs and Water heater. All less than 16 months. Large fenced yard, finished basement with 2nd kitchen ! Lots of storage, walk in closets, and more room to grown. New exterior trim paint and some interior trim as well.  This home has hardwood floors, tile and wall to wall carpet- A John Wieland Swim and Tennis neighborhood. Won't last ! Lost of square footage ! Open House Sunday, Nov 15, from 2-5.
